Viewed Hey everyone, hope you are all doing well! It's been a while since I last posted an update, Joshua Shaw  and I have been hard at work on our new feature-film length crossover, "Convergent Chaos"!! I understand the wait has been a lot longer than normal for a new video, but we are striving to make it worth the wait!! This collaboration will be the culmination of months of story planning, scripting, recording, editing, and all the good stuff that goes into making our favorite Presidents come to life!

We (of course) have no concrete release date, but are working hard to get it out (hopefully) sometime before the end of the year! Again, although it has been a very long wait since the Presidents' last adventure, we aim to completely blow the first crossover out of the water, and it sure will!

Along with that, many of you have been asking when or if I will cover Black Ops 6, and the answer is of course yes. Normal videos will resume after the collab, with The Presidential Zomboys continuing their original schedule of Zombies (finishing Black Ops 1, WAW, BO4 Chaos, IW, Cold War, etc.) but they will also be covering Black Ops 6 very soon after normal videos resume, so it won't get pushed till the end.

I just want to thank you all for the continued support for the Zomboys in general, and the patience in waiting for Convergent Chaos, we are extremely excited to finally have you all view it! Thank you all so much!!
